channel.title: My Work 2 Hours Ago
channel.description:
I have just started coding Ado-Pkz V1.
[b][i][u]New Features[/u][/i][/b]
[b][i]SYIPkPker Blocker Added
Removed Castlewars So People May Not Access Staff Area
Edited Staff Zone
Added 1 New Store At Staff Zone
Added to Block Name With Symbols Such As "?" "@" "$"
A Custom Maze Minigame. At the end you get a random reward. Made with hedges, fountains, trees, fences, and fill with a few Npcs. More Npcs you kill the better reward is.
New Starter Pack
3 More Shops
Fun Zone
New Starter Outfit[/i][/b]
[b][i][u]Soon To Be Added[/u][/i][/b]
[b][i] Custom Godsword Minigame
Webclient
Fix Beards
Custom Character Clothes When Started. [/i][/b]
[b][size=10pt][size=10pt]I don't want to show pictures. I want people to wait till I'm done.
Please tell me if I am doing good or bad Coding my Server So Far.[/size][/size][/b]
